name: For What Was
description:
This is for anyone who has a hard time expressing themselves through art due to trauma. 

If you buy one on either primary or secondary and then mint anything based on post-traumatic stress, let me know on Twitter @ConvallariaNFTs; I'll retweet your project and airdrop a free "I see it, but how do I get there?" from my ocean series to your collection. 

Offer stands until the last edition in my possession is given away.
